## Prerequisites

- Python 3.14+
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)

## Setup

```bash
uv sync
```

## Configuration

### Claude Desktop

Add to `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ service_slug }}": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": ["{{ package_name }}"]
    }
  }
}
```

### Claude Code

```bash
claude mcp add {{ service_slug }} -- uvx {{ package_name }}
```

